About Me

Hello! I am Krishna Sai Surendra Kalluri, a talented Front End Engineer with a passion for building cutting-edge web and mobile applications using React.js and React-Native frameworks. With an extensive knowledge of HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React/Redux, Redux Saga, ES6, jQuery, Bootstrap, NodeJS, Styled Components, SASS/LESS CSS Preprocessors, and RESTful web services, I am a versatile and skilled professional who has proven my expertise time and again.


I am a self-driven individual who is always eager to learn and explore new things. I possess a sharp mind and can quickly adapt to changing trends and technologies in the industry. With my ability to think out of the box and a keen eye for detail, I am capable of building constructive and efficient solutions that can meet the unique needs of my clients.


I strongly believe that open-mindedness is the key to creativity and gaining insight into any subject in my area. I approach each project with a fresh perspective and take the time to understand my client's requirements to deliver high-quality work that exceeds their expectations.


If you're looking for a skilled and dedicated Front End Engineer who can help you build web and mobile applications that are fast, efficient, and visually appealing, then I am the right person for you!
